AWRD.ST.summary: Awardit AB (publ) operates a loyalty platform in Sweden. It offers customer clubs, loyalty programs, sales motivation programs, digital scoring currencies, and scorers solutions. The company was founded in 1999 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.

T1D.F.summary: TradeDoubler AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, provides performance-based digital marketing services and technology solutions for publishers and advertisers worldwide. It offers affiliate marketing solutions; white-label partner management platform to manage and run affiliate network; full service programmatic solutions to identify and connect with new customers; and campaign management solutions. The company also provides Metapic, a platform for product recommendations that helps advertisers and digital creatives to enhance through reader engaging content. In addition, it offers tracking solutions, such as global, cookie less, cross device, voucher code, product level, and call tracking, as well as container tag solutions; and integration solutions, including products, vouchers, conversions, and claims APIs. TradeDoubler AB (publ) was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. TradeDoubler AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Reworld Media S.A.

Z03.F.summary: ZetaDisplay AB (publ) provides digital signage solutions. The company also offers ZetaDisplay Engage CMS platform; and ZetaTouch, a service that links the physical store with its e-commerce. It serves retail, automotive, banking and finance, corporate communication, transportation, public sector, gaming and lottery, and fashion industries, as well as convenience stores, fast food centers, and restaurants.
